I"Ž<h1 id="leave-encashment">Leave Encashment</h1>

<h2 id="add">Add</h2>

<p><strong>STEP-1</strong>: Select <strong>Add Leave Encashment</strong> in the menu. <strong>LeaveNCash</strong> window will appear.</p>

<p><strong>STEP-2</strong>: Fill the date and click on Get <strong>Leaves Record</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="" alt="" /></p>

<p><img src="" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-3</strong>: Click on <strong>Save</strong> button.</p>

<h2 id="list">List</h2>

<p>Browse employee and select Leaves Ledger. You can see the list of leave encashment.</p>

<p><img src="" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="edit">Edit</h2>

<p>Browse employee and select <strong>Leaves Ledger</strong>. Right click on Earned Leave Encashment and select <strong>Edit Leave Encashment</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>Leave Encashment</strong> form will appear. Edit the details and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>
